---
# design.md sec 3.4: COO delivers the distributed-tracing console UIPlugin.
# sec 9 "Support status": this is gated on the COO plugin's published support
# status for the target OpenShift version; the Tempo Route below remains the
# supported per-cluster break-glass UI if the console plugin is unavailable.
apiVersion: observability.openshift.io/v1alpha1
kind: UIPlugin
metadata:
  name: distributed-tracing
spec:
  type: DistributedTracing
